Note 2. Except as provided herein, the MU-2 District has no maximum building height; provided,
however, that if adjacent to a structure of a lesser building height in an adjoining zoning district, the
maximum height shall be 75 feet at the setback plus one foot of increased height for each two feet of
additional setback.
llm_outputs.rationale: The MU-2 District's maximum building height is described in Note 2, which states that there is generally no limit except under specific conditions related to adjacent structures.
llm_outputs.answer: No limit; 75 feet at the setback plus one foot for each two feet of additional setback when adjacent to a lesser height structure
